snippet.title: Paladin's Passage Launch Trailer PS5 Game
snippet.description:
The ultimate "block-buster" 2.5D platformer game Paladin's Passage is available NOW on PS5.
Embark on an epic journey where you create and destroy blocks to navigate through 140 levels of magic and danger.
Every block you add or remove changes the flow of the game.
Now's the time to Block'n'Roll at https://www.paladinspassage.com
